title: Most favorite lyrics?
body:
Mine go like this lol

"I'm way too gone,wtf am I doing,wake up in the morning who the fuck am I screwing,my partners on brown and you know I'm on white,you know it's going down I can do this all night. Gotta get to the paper,one time for the haters,money over bitches two times for the fakers because even in the dark baby Imma shown bright,way too gone best night of my life." - From Way Too Gone by Young Jeezy. I seriously can't go a day without listening to that song on repeat a few times lol Its my goto song after waking up every morning.
